{"tid":884521,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"而家有幾多人係會 先出後入？","createTime":"2018-10-31T16:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T16:12:17.000Z","uid":158245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a3779faa32691f451bc06bc9edc53cff500a1bd1","tid":884521,"uid":158245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:03:27.000Z","msg":"頭先搭地鐵返屋企，<br />\n到站果時己經見到有2條友係月台企正門口<br />\n開左門 佢地都冇意識擋住左人，要讓人落左車先<br />\n然後我行前左一步，企左係度唔郁（睇佢咩反應<br />\n點知個啊嬸格硬 打側行入車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後同行麻甩佬仲係咁啤住我<br />\n雖然冇法例係一定要比人出左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但正常禮儀啦<br />\n係d 廢老唔識 定 而家d人 都唔會讓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e206656bd63d7d3156ae9d011e0931f886e47f","tid":884521,"uid":158245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}